<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GLAB 대여 현황</title>
  
  <!-- Google Fonts: Noto Sans KR -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    .noto-sans-kr-regular {
      font-family: "Noto Sans KR", serif;
      font-optical-sizing: auto;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: normal;
    }
    body {
      font-family: "Noto Sans KR", serif;
      background-color: #232323;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    /* 배너 이미지 (필요 시 수정) */
    .banner {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 2 / 1;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .banner img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      margin: 0;
    }
    header h2 {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin: 5px 0 0;
      color: #bbb;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      header h1 {
        font-size: 1.8em;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
      header h2 {
        font-size: 1em;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
    }
    hr {
      border: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: #666;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .room-section {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    /* 방 이름을 감싸는 둥근 박스 */
    .room-box {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    /* GLAB1, GLAB2에 맞는 색상 지정 (예시) */
    .room-glab1 {
    background-color: #4B0082; /* 어두운 인디고 */
    color: #ffffff;
    }
    .room-glab2 {
    background-color: #800080; /* 약간 밝은 보라 */
    color: #ffffff;
    }

    /* 예약 목록 박스 (모든 예약을 감싸는 둥근 박스) */
    .reservation-box {
      background: #333;
      border: 1px solid #444;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    /* 예약 테이블 스타일 (3열: 예약 시간, 예약 번호, 신청자) */
    .reservation-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .reservation-table td {
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #bbb;
    }
    .reservation-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      text-align: center;
      color: #bbb;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="noto-sans-kr-regular">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- 배너 이미지 (필요 시 적용) -->
    <div class="banner">
      <img src="/img/2.jpg" alt="Banner">
    </div>
    
    <header>
      <h1>GLAB</h1>
      <h2>금일 예약 현황 (<%= today %>)</h2>
    </header>
    
    <hr>
    
    <!-- GLAB1 예약 섹션 -->
    <section class="room-section">
      <div class="room-box room-glab1">GLAB1</div>
      <div class="reservation-box">
        <table class="reservation-table">
          <tbody>
            <% if (reservations["glab1"] && reservations["glab1"].length > 0) { %>
              <% reservations["glab1"].forEach(reservation => { %>
                <tr>
                  <td><%= reservation.time %></td>
                  <td><%= reservation.code %></td>
                  <td><%= reservation.name %></td>
                </tr>
              <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
              <tr><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
            <% } %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- GLAB2 예약 섹션 -->
    <section class="room-section">
      <div class="room-box room-glab2">GLAB2</div>
      <div class="reservation-box">
        <table class="reservation-table">
          <tbody>
            <% if (reservations["glab2"] && reservations["glab2"].length > 0) { %>
              <% reservations["glab2"].forEach(reservation => { %>
                <tr>
                  <td><%= reservation.time %></td>
                  <td><%= reservation.code %></td>
                  <td><%= reservation.name %></td>
                </tr>
              <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
              <tr><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
            <% } %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        교내 시설물 대여 시스템이 구축되기 전까지 교학지원팀으로부터 관리를 위임 받아<br>
        학생회에서 임시로 운영 중인 시스템입니다.
      </p>
      <hr>
      <p>
        ©중앙대학교 예술공학대학 학생회. All Rights Reserved. | <a href="https://pf.kakao.com/_TzxirG">문의사항</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        Powered By <a href="https://www.instagram.com/team.doob?igsh=MXNxdnJpaDgzengwZQ%3D%3D&utm_source=qr">Team d{OO}b</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
